    "image-gallery": {
      "type": "image--gallery",
      "blocks": {
        "gallery-0": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/7179ab78-f39d-42a7-b28c-f3e0647dae22.jpg",
            "link": "",
            "title": "Alex",
            "subheading": "I decided to get my first fur baby from My Felidae since they offered such gorgeous kittens. They were thoroughly responsive and communicated quickly, answering any concerns and questions I had about my kitten. They made things very simple and accessible which made for a very smooth process. I’d highly recommend and will be getting my fur baby a best friend from My Felidae soon :)",
            "overlay-btn-text": "",
            "show-gradient-overlay": true,
            "overlay_font_color": "#ffffff",
            "overlay_color": "#1f1f1f"
          }
        },
        "gallery-1": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/dcbbdd2c-3f69-44ea-9ecf-049d25dcac45.jpg",
            "link": "",
            "title": "Maariyah",
            "subheading": "I'm so thankful for My Felidae. I have my dream kitten because of them & will be forever grateful for that. She's my perfect little fur baby and I love her so much. We're a perfect match, she loves cuddles and is the most playful cat. My Felidae made the process so  simple and you can tell how much love and care there is for every kitten they have. I'll forever be grateful that I found my sweet malala through them!",
            "overlay-btn-text": "",
            "show-gradient-overlay": true,
            "overlay_font_color": "#ffffff",
            "overlay_color": "#1f1f1f"
          }
        },
        "gallery-2": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/5f635857-143a-4342-9cae-6a3f2f95e213.jpg",
            "link": "",
            "title": "Taylor",
            "subheading": "I am so thankful for Marina!!!Without her, I would have never found my gorgeous Scottish Fold, Bella! When I first found her account on instagram, I figured I would reach out and feel out the situation, not knowing how legit everything was. Maria immediately gave me her personal contact information and set up calls and face times so that I could see the kittens and get to know her! She is literally so kind and helpful. I must say… I was rather picky when it came to the cat I wanted and she did everything and some to help me find my love! Thank you Maria for your help!",
            "overlay-btn-text": "",
            "show-gradient-overlay": true,
            "overlay_font_color": "#ffffff",
            "overlay_color": "#1f1f1f"
          }
        },
        "gallery-3": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "image": "shopify://shop_images/9d48d34e-5f1c-4b18-b721-c0a5e64e4262.jpg",
            "link": "",
            "title": "Uzma",
            "subheading": "Found My Felidae via Instagram and fell in love with all the cats pictured but one cat in particular caught my family’s eye. After chatting with the seller Maria regarding the cat my husband and I decided to put our deposit on the kitten. We waited about a week and a half till the kitten  landed in Los Angeles.  Finally the big day arrived to meet our new Furry family member! My family and I traveled 4+ hours away from up north to down south to pick up and meet our Kitten for the first time.  I have to say, We were so pleased with our new kitten.  We couldn’t have picked a better kitten or seller. Maria from My Felidae was amazing at communicating regarding the cat, when it was set to fly and arrive. Our kitten pictured was exactly what we received. We picked the best cat and we’re so blessed to have her part of our family. Our kitten is friendly, loving, super playful, healthy, has amazing temperament and the best companion to our toddler. I highly recommend My Felidae to everyone when purchasing a cat. Very secure and trusted cat broker. Thank you My Felidae we love our Kitten!",
            "overlay-btn-text": "",
            "show-gradient-overlay": true,
            "overlay_font_color": "#ffffff",
            "overlay_color": "#1f1f1f"
          }
        }
      },
